EXECUTIVE OVERVIEW
Cigna Corporation, together with its subsidiaries (either individually or collectively referred to as "Cigna," the "Company," "we,"
"our" or "us") is a global health services organization with a mission of helping those we serve improve their health, well-being and
peace of mind by making health care affordable, predictable and simple. Our subsidiaries offer a differentiated set of pharmacy,
medical, dental and related products and services. For further information on our business and strategy, see Item 1, "Business" in this
Form 10-K.
